short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Mixpanel Dashboard for easy debug

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A tool to track the mixpanel requests in your webpage during debugging the data issue. It automatically decodes the Mixpanel tag to make it easy to view. You can find the Mixpanel debugger in Developer Tools window.
